r affiliated with Apte Pro. His real name was Takaya Katō (加藤 孝也 Katō Takaya).","name":"Takaya Hashi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"土师孝也，日本资深男性声优，毕业于武藏工业大学附属高等学校与桐朋学园艺术短期大学；以醇正而浑厚的低音而著称，常配稳健的角色，有时也配恶役。\n\n土师孝也代表作品有《纯洁的玛利亚》、《亚尔斯兰战记》、《潮与虎》等。","name":"土师孝也","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"土師孝也","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Takaya Hashi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"하시 타카야","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Такая Хаси","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Takaja Haši","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Takaya Hashi (土師 孝也 Hashi Takaya, nacido el 8 de septiembre de 1952) es un veterano actor de doblaje y actor japonés  afiliado a Apte Pro. Su verdadero nombre es Takaya Katō (加藤 孝也 Katō Takaya).","name":"Takaya Hashi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ทากายะ ฮาชิ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Такая Хаші","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"土師孝也，男，日本資深男性聲優，畢業於武藏工業大學附屬高等學校與桐朋學園藝術短期大學；以醇正而渾厚的低音而著稱，常配穩健的角色，有時也配惡役。\n\n土師孝也代表作品有《純潔的瑪利亞》、《亞爾斯蘭戰記》、《潮與虎》等。","name":"土師孝也","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"